---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/astro/Breadcrumbs.astro";

const crumbs = [
  { name: "Home", path: "/" },
  { name: "Affiliate Disclosure", path: "/affiliate-disclosure" },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — MatchFluent"
  description="How MatchFluent makes money: which links are affiliate links, what we earn, and why commissions never change our recommendations."
  path="/affiliate-disclosure"
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">
    <Breadcrumbs {crumbs} />
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-navy-700 mb-6">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

    <article class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg text-navy-700">
        MatchFluent is reader-supported. Some links on this site are affiliate links: if you click
        one and make a purchase, we earn a commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-navy-700 pt-2">Which links are affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Links to Rocket Languages (Rocket English) are affiliate links, operated through affiliate
        networks such as Awin. When we add other partner programs (for example, tutoring platforms
        or exam-prep tools), those links will be affiliate links too, and this page will list them.
        Links to free resources — Duolingo, BBC Learning English, VOA Learning English, Anki,
        LibriVox and similar — earn us nothing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-navy-700 pt-2">
        Why commissions don't change our recommendations
      </h2>
      <p>
        Our reviews follow a fixed methodology — see
        <a href="/how-we-review/" class="text-teal-700 underline">how we review</a> — applied before
        any monetization question. We routinely recommend free tools over paid ones where they're the
        better fit, state the limits of the products we earn from, and mark every affiliate CTA
        clearly. A short disclosure appears near the top of every page containing affiliate links.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-navy-700 pt-2">FTC compliance</h2>
      <p>
        This disclosure is made in accordance with the U.S. Federal Trade Commission's guidelines on
        endorsements and testimonials (16 CFR Part 255) and the terms of the affiliate networks we
        participate in.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm">
        En español: algunos enlaces de MatchFluent son enlaces de afiliado — si compras a través de
        ellos, recibimos una comisión sin costo extra para ti. Nuestras recomendaciones siguen una
        <a href="/como-evaluamos/" class="text-teal-700 underline">metodología fija</a> que las
        comisiones nunca alteran.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
